snippet.title: Unlich Demo Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Finally i'd like to welcome to Unlich, a dark fantasy monster-taming RPG! The demo is finally available on Itch, hope you like and if you have any feedback, I'd be thankfull if you could send it my way on Discord or Twitter.

Follow me:

Itch.io: https://hawmaro.itch.io/unlich
Twitter: https://twitter.com/HAWmaro
Discord: https://discord.gg/Bnwx3ntj
